article.description: — Ebby Asamoah had 14 points as Delaware rolled past Elon 66-43 on Saturday.
article.headline: Asamoah scores 14 to lead Delaware past Elon 66-43
article.linkText: Asamoah scores 14 to lead Delaware past Elon 66-43
article.story: NEWARK, Del. -- — Ebby Asamoah had 14 points as Delaware rolled past Elon 66-43 on Saturday. Kevin Anderson had 11 points for Delaware (6-7, 4-4 Colonial Athletic Association). Dylan Painter added 10 rebounds and five assists. Andrew Carr had seven rebounds. Hunter McIntosh had 10 points for the Phoenix (3-4, 0-3), whose losing streak reached four games. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
